## Limitations

The findings are based on available data up to October 2023 and may not reflect the most current legislative changes or emerging research. Additionally, the perspectives gathered are primarily from U.S.-based sources, which may not fully represent global views on the issue. Further research could explore international policies and cultural differences in social media usage among minors.